284
00:17:28,472 --> 00:17:30,871
Yes. It was all to make it look

285
00:17:30,872 --> 00:17:33,771
as if you were favoring just that girl

286
00:17:33,772 --> 00:17:36,371
so the other children would resent her

287
00:17:36,372 --> 00:17:40,371
