325
00:19:38,572 --> 00:19:42,671
People living in Hokkaido rarely use umbrellas when it snows.

326
00:19:42,672 --> 00:19:48,471
If so, it is more likely that she grew up in a place other than Hokkaido.

327
00:19:48,472 --> 00:19:52,771
Moreover, she said that the last dialogue in my novel

328
00:19:52,772 --> 00:19:56,171
