329
00:19:56,172 --> 00:19:57,172
"The Missing Body, Yusaku Kudo"

330
00:19:57,173 --> 00:19:58,771
In that novel,

331
00:19:58,772 --> 00:20:03,671
the detective finds a runaway girl who faked her suicide,

332
00:20:03,672 --> 00:20:07,671
