333
00:20:07,672 --> 00:20:12,171
in order to convince her to return to her parent.

334
00:20:12,172 --> 00:20:14,771
If those words moved her,

335
00:20:14,772 --> 00:20:18,172
I figured maybe she was also a runaway.

336
00:20:19,272 --> 00:20:21,671
If you want to see your daughter,

337
00:20:21,672 --> 00:20:23,471
go on and turn yourself in, too.

338
00:20:23,472 --> 00:20:29,472
Before my friends who are staking out get impatient.

